      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "For reference, the assert in `sync.cpp` has been changed to `std::abort` in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/11640#discussion_r154455316\r\n\r\nDestructors are not called on `std::abort`, see https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/utility/program/abort\r\n\r\nThus, the thread group keeps running forever: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/442a9c64775454a7073aff9872721c58b1dd35c5/src/test/setup_common.cpp#L111-L114",
